                          agriculteur ayant fait ses &eacute;tudes aux USA<br>
                        </b>Voir : <a
href="http://www.truthabouttrade.org/news/editorials/guest-commentary/16820-standing-up-against-gene-ocide">http://www.truthabouttrade.org/news/editorials/<br>
guest-commentary/16820-standing-up-against-gene-ocide</a><br>
